data.description: PRICE REDUCED with motivated sellers!!! Beautiful home on over 2 acres with a private country feel but also close to town. 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 bonus rooms have potential of 6 bedrooms with 3.5 bathrooms! 2.5 bathrooms downstairs and a full bath upstairs that's recently been remodeled! The home also has a large storm shelter in basement for the safety of your family. A newer roof and granite countertops takes two things to worry about off your list. The manicured yard features beautiful mature landscaping including peach, apple, and pear trees. This home is perfect for your growing family or if you just want some space. Call Cort today for your private showing!
